00:13:24,970 --> 00:13:26,210
I was busy cooking.

296
00:13:26,410 --> 00:13:27,990
I forgot to bring your bag here.

297
00:13:27,990 --> 00:13:29,110
Did you cook again?

298
00:13:29,620 --> 00:13:30,550
Yes, I want to

299
00:13:30,550 --> 00:13:31,390
thank you.

300
00:13:31,390 --> 00:13:32,880
I just learnt a new dish.

301
00:13:33,270 --> 00:13:34,310
Don't mention it.

302
00:13:34,310 --> 00:13:35,470
Thank you so much.

303
00:13:35,490 --> 00:13:36,180
Mr. Jia.

304
00:13:36,470 --> 00:13:37,730
Let's go to the office.

305
00:13:40,060 --> 00:13:40,790
Come with me.

306
00:13:44,100 --> 00:13:44,830
What a waste.

307
00:13:45,800 --> 00:13:47,030
Director Xiao, let me help you.

308
00:13:47,030 --> 00:13:48,230
Don't bother. Go ahead with your work.

309
00:13:48,230 --> 00:13:49,020
Okay.

310
00:13:50,620 --> 00:13:51,860
Nice to meet you.

311
00:13:55,610 --> 00:13:56,740
Come here, Baoshan.

312
00:13:56,990 --> 00:13:58,160
Please come in.

313
00:13:58,980 --> 00:14:00,500
Make yourself at home.

314
00:14:06,670 --> 00:14:07,590
It's noon.

315
00:14:07,590 --> 00:14:10,300
Won't teachers and students come here after their classes?

316
00:14:10,300 --> 00:14:11,310
This is Director's Office.

317
00:14:11,310 --> 00:14:13,620
The faculty won't come here unless they have something to deal with.

318
00:14:13,620 --> 00:14:14,680
Please have a seat.

319
00:14:14,750 --> 00:14:15,440
Make yourself at home.

320
00:14:15,440 --> 00:14:15,830
Okay.

321
00:14:18,480 --> 00:14:19,480
Look at you.

322
00:14:19,550 --> 00:14:20,990
We are friends.

323
00:14:20,990 --> 00:14:22,550
Why bother cooking so many dishes?

324
00:14:22,550 --> 00:14:24,610
I do not consider myself an outsider.

325
00:14:26,140 --> 00:14:26,750
Here.

326
00:14:27,340 --> 00:14:28,210
Have some water.

327
00:14:28,210 --> 00:14:28,940
Thank you.

328
00:14:30,310 --> 00:14:31,950
Then I'll try the dish now.

329
00:14:32,310 --> 00:14:34,040
I'll try it before it gets cold.

330
00:14:36,690 --> 00:14:38,610
You are so considerate, Baoshan.

331
00:14:40,250 --> 00:14:42,450
You even packed it with a handkerchief.

332
00:14:47,600 --> 00:14:48,590
What is this?

333
00:14:48,730 --> 00:14:49,930
The Eight-Treasure Duck.

334
00:14:49,930 --> 00:14:52,350
There are eight precious ingredients in it.

335
00:14:52,350 --> 00:14:54,670
I know you have been busy

336
00:14:54,670 --> 00:14:55,710
and working hard all the time.

337
00:14:55,710 --> 00:14:57,190
So I learnt this dish

338
00:14:57,190 --> 00:14:59,050
which can replenish your energy.

339
00:15:10,600 --> 00:15:11,360
Delicious.

340
00:15:11,910 --> 00:15:13,640
Why is it so sweet?

341
00:15:13,960 --> 00:15:15,880
It is Shanghai cuisine.

342
00:15:17,320 --> 00:15:19,390
You could have just cooked local dishes,

343
00:15:19,390 --> 00:15:22,590
but you invested your energy in making Shanghai cuisine.

344
00:15:24,990 --> 00:15:25,980
Eat less.

345
00:15:27,570 --> 00:15:28,980
Take your time.

346
00:15:29,640 --> 00:15:30,430
Sure.

347
00:15:32,920 --> 00:15:33,560
Director.

348
00:15:36,000 --> 00:15:37,460
Ms. Han, class dismissed?

349
00:15:38,310 --> 00:15:39,670
Hello, Mr. Jia.

350
00:15:40,550 --> 00:15:41,390
Baoshan

351
00:15:41,390 --> 00:15:43,270
learned to cook a new dish, Eight-Treasure Duck.

352
00:15:43,270 --> 00:15:45,330
He brought it here to let me have a try.

353
00:15:45,530 --> 00:15:46,790
What's wrong, Ms. Han?

354
00:15:47,020 --> 00:15:47,990
Nothing serious.

355
00:15:47,990 --> 00:15:48,950
I would like to know the arrangement

356
00:15:48,950 --> 00:15:50,310
for the final exam.

357
00:15:51,260 --> 00:15:52,510
Arrangement for the final exam?

358
00:15:52,510 --> 00:15:54,310
I'll send it to you all tomorrow.

359
00:15:54,510 --> 00:15:55,390
You came at the right time.

360
00:15:55,390 --> 00:15:56,550
Join us and have a try.

361
00:15:56,550 --> 00:15:57,100
Yes.

362
00:15:57,240 --> 00:15:59,360
Thank you, Director. I'm not hungry.

363
00:15:59,830 --> 00:16:01,430
You have to try it.

364
00:16:01,470 --> 00:16:02,150
I used

365
00:16:02,150 --> 00:16:03,060
the best ingredients.

366
00:16:03,060 --> 00:16:03,910
My cooking skills

367
00:16:03,910 --> 00:16:05,340
are as good as Shanghai locals.

368
00:16:05,340 --> 00:16:06,870
It's good for your stomach.

369
00:16:07,310 --> 00:16:08,350
Mr. Jia.

370
00:16:08,480 --> 00:16:10,480
Don't force her if she's not hungry.

371
00:16:11,050 --> 00:16:11,800
Ms. Han.

372
00:16:12,070 --> 00:16:13,190
The winter vacation is coming.

373
00:16:13,190 --> 00:16:14,470
Don't slack off.

374
00:16:14,470 --> 00:16:15,270
Kids tend to

375
00:16:15,270 --> 00:16:16,650
get distracted by the upcoming vacation.

376
00:16:16,650 --> 00:16:17,980
Don't worry, Director.

377
00:16:18,230 --> 00:16:19,870
I'll go back now.

378
00:16:19,870 --> 00:16:20,270
Okay.

379
00:16:20,270 --> 00:16:21,270
Enjoy your meal.

380
00:16:24,960 --> 00:16:25,870
Have a seat, Baoshan.

381
00:16:25,870 --> 00:16:26,530
Have a seat.

382
00:16:28,750 --> 00:16:29,550
Why don't you try it?

383
00:16:29,550 --> 00:16:30,590
I... I...

384
00:16:30,590 --> 00:16:31,560
I don't like sweet food.

385
00:16:31,560 --> 00:16:32,240
Really?

386
00:16:33,870 --> 00:16:34,670
May I come in?

387
00:16:35,600 --> 00:16:36,230
Yes.

388
00:16:40,790 --> 00:16:41,590
Director agreed

389
00:16:41,590 --> 00:16:43,080
to let Hua'er take an exam.

390
00:16:43,550 --> 00:16:44,550
As long as she passes the exam,

391
00:16:44,550 --> 00:16:45,590
we can negotiate with the principal

392
00:16:45,590 --> 00:16:46,520
with her grades.

393
00:16:47,620 --> 00:16:48,950
Isn't my aunt reliable?

394
00:16:49,120 --> 00:16:50,520
She will also be my aunt.

395
00:16:51,000 --> 00:16:51,640
By the way,

396
00:16:51,910 --> 00:16:52,990
these are the textbooks and test papers I found

397
00:16:52,990 --> 00:16:54,080
from the Junior High School Department.

398
00:16:54,080 --> 00:16:55,060
Take them back to Hua'er

399
00:16:55,060 --> 00:16:56,990
and ask her to review accordingly.

400
00:16:57,350 --> 00:16:58,670
This is a rare opportunity.

401
00:16:58,670 --> 00:16:59,590
Help her

402
00:16:59,610 --> 00:17:00,670
when you have time.

403
00:17:03,400 --> 00:17:04,460
Thank you, Mr. Gao.

404
00:17:06,650 --> 00:17:07,310
Look at you.

405
00:17:07,319 --> 00:17:08,849
How many times have I told you?

406
00:17:08,849 --> 00:17:09,510
Look at you.

407
00:17:09,510 --> 00:17:11,390
Can't you take good care of yourself?

408
00:17:11,390 --> 00:17:12,869
You've suffered from stomach illness

409
00:17:12,869 --> 00:17:14,150
since you were young.

410
00:17:14,859 --> 00:17:16,589
Can't you be more careful?

411
00:17:17,030 --> 00:17:18,220
Don't sit here.

412
00:17:18,460 --> 00:17:19,470
Director

413
00:17:19,470 --> 00:17:20,150
will come here for patrol later.

414
00:17:20,150 --> 00:17:21,450
Well, it's inappropriate for you to sit here.

415
00:17:21,450 --> 00:17:22,450
Sit here. Come on.

416
00:17:23,990 --> 00:17:25,119
What should I do now?

417
00:17:27,109 --> 00:17:28,710
I still have to drink when it's necessary.

418
00:17:28,710 --> 00:17:30,480
I can't say I agree with you.

419
00:17:30,620 --> 00:17:32,280
Do you have to drink like that?

420
00:17:35,080 --> 00:17:36,070
Well, if you

421
00:17:36,110 --> 00:17:37,030
do what you should do at work,

422
00:17:37,030 --> 00:17:38,150
leaders won't pick holes

423
00:17:38,150 --> 00:17:40,010
or judge you about your drinking.

424
00:17:40,530 --> 00:17:41,990
After you drink with this leader today,

425
00:17:41,990 --> 00:17:43,610
you'll drink with another one tomorrow.

426
00:17:43,610 --> 00:17:44,630
You just want

427
00:17:44,630 --> 00:17:45,590
to get along well with leaders

428
00:17:45,590 --> 00:17:46,790
and take some shortcuts, don't you?

429
00:17:46,790 --> 00:17:48,270
I don't think this is advisable,

430
00:17:48,270 --> 00:17:48,830
you know?

431
00:17:48,830 --> 00:17:49,670
And such leaders

432
00:17:49,670 --> 00:17:50,430
will find trouble for themselves sooner or later.

433
00:17:50,430 --> 00:17:51,360
I don't think their behaviors are advisable either.

434
00:17:51,360 --> 00:17:52,960
Yes, I shouldn't drink.

435
00:17:53,270 --> 00:17:54,070
But I should take the medicine.

436
00:17:54,070 --> 00:17:54,660
Hurry up.

437
00:17:54,660 --> 00:17:55,710
It hurts so much.

438
00:17:55,710 --> 00:17:57,070
I'm just an ENT specialist.

439
00:17:57,070 --> 00:17:58,090
What medicine should I get for you?

440
00:17:58,090 --> 00:17:59,010
Open-throat sword spray

441
00:17:59,010 --> 00:17:59,820
or nasal relief?

442
00:17:59,820 --> 00:18:00,870
Can they cure your stomachache?

443
00:18:00,870 --> 00:18:01,870
Well, don't you

444
00:18:01,870 --> 00:18:02,550
get along well with the female gastroenterologist?

445
00:18:02,550 --> 00:18:03,330
You can get her help through the back door.

446
00:18:03,330 --> 00:18:04,530
Don't talk nonsense.

447
00:18:05,360 --> 00:18:06,220
Well, let's go.

448
00:18:06,470 --> 00:18:08,070
Wait a minute. Wait a minute.

449
00:18:08,320 --> 00:18:09,910
Who is this again?

450
00:18:11,990 --> 00:18:13,550
Are you going or not? Don't you have a stomachache?

451
00:18:13,550 --> 00:18:15,210
I'm always busy making calls.

452
00:18:24,910 --> 00:18:26,430
This is an internal line.

453
00:18:27,230 --> 00:18:29,030
Only internal calls can be made.

454
00:18:31,070 --> 00:18:32,330
Your rank is still low.

455
00:18:33,150 --> 00:18:34,230
You are rich now,

456
00:18:34,230 --> 00:18:35,430
yet you still want to take advantage of others.

457
00:18:35,430 --> 00:18:36,030
It's been years.

458
00:18:36,030 --> 00:18:39,360
Why haven't they installed an external line in your office?

459
00:18:43,130 --> 00:18:44,060
Secretary Wang.

460
00:18:45,130 --> 00:18:46,130
Volleyball game?

461
00:18:47,900 --> 00:18:49,460
I must be the one who leads the team.

462
00:18:49,460 --> 00:18:50,000
Well.

463
00:18:50,230 --> 00:18:51,870
I'm not scrambling.

464
00:18:51,870 --> 00:18:53,910
I... Do you want to be the champion?

465
00:18:54,570 --> 00:18:56,510
I have to be the leader if you want to win a championship.

466
00:18:56,510 --> 00:18:57,510
I'm capable

467
00:18:57,510 --> 00:18:59,140
of stirring up the atmosphere.

468
00:18:59,140 --> 00:19:00,220
So annoying.

469
00:19:00,290 --> 00:19:01,420
Damn it.

470
00:19:01,710 --> 00:19:02,710
I spent so much money

471
00:19:02,710 --> 00:19:03,690
and so much energy.

472
00:19:03,690 --> 00:19:05,170
But you ate everything!

473
00:19:05,510 --> 00:19:07,780
A duck weighing 1.5 kilometers with ingredients weighing one kilometer.

474
00:19:07,780 --> 00:19:09,260
There was nothing left!

475
00:19:09,410 --> 00:19:11,470
Can you tell if it's delicious or not?

476
00:19:11,980 --> 00:19:13,070
The more you eat, the fatter you'll be

477
00:19:13,070 --> 00:19:15,000
and the less attractive you'll be.

478
00:19:22,520 --> 00:19:23,640
Hua'er, let's eat.

479
00:19:24,990 --> 00:19:27,590
Brother, what's the school like over there?

480
00:19:28,490 --> 00:19:29,820
It's big and beautiful.

481
00:19:30,410 --> 00:19:32,730
Will they look down on us?

482
00:19:34,030 --> 00:19:34,740
No.

483
00:19:35,530 --> 00:19:37,030
I saw the clothes

484
00:19:37,060 --> 00:19:38,830
your classmates wore before.

485
00:19:39,110 --> 00:19:40,370
They're so beautiful.

486
00:19:40,730 --> 00:19:42,280
So are their shoes.

487
00:19:42,510 --> 00:19:44,590
Those white tourist shoes

488
00:19:44,620 --> 00:19:45,830
looked expensive.

489
00:19:46,250 --> 00:19:48,500
I dare not talk to her.

490
00:19:50,150 --> 00:19:52,390
Actually, she's very nice.

491
00:19:52,750 --> 00:19:53,750
You'll know

492
00:19:53,750 --> 00:19:55,410
after you get into the school.

493
00:19:56,110 --> 00:19:57,720
Are you guys

494
00:19:57,720 --> 00:19:59,060
friends now?

495
00:20:01,270 --> 00:20:02,310
Kind of.

496
00:20:03,580 --> 00:20:05,110
When I worked

497
00:20:05,110 --> 00:20:06,310
in the restaurant,

498
00:20:06,710 --> 00:20:08,050
I saw the kids who came from the city

499
00:20:08,050 --> 00:20:09,480
celebrate their birthdays.

500
00:20:09,480 --> 00:20:11,710
They even ate a two-layer cake.

501
00:20:11,710 --> 00:20:13,270
I hadn't seen one before.

502
00:20:14,320 --> 00:20:16,560
My boss's daughter was nice to me.

503
00:20:16,950 --> 00:20:18,190
She even bought me

504
00:20:18,190 --> 00:20:19,360
a boxed ice cream.

505
00:20:20,550 --> 00:20:22,800
I dare not talk to her.

506
00:20:23,000 --> 00:20:25,060
I was afraid she would look down on me.

507
00:20:26,330 --> 00:20:27,570
At first,

508
00:20:28,440 --> 00:20:29,790
I thought so too.

509
00:20:32,460 --> 00:20:34,750
Not long ago, it was her little brother's birthday.

510
00:20:34,750 --> 00:20:35,860
I had nothing to offer him as a present.

511
00:20:35,860 --> 00:20:37,350
So I gave him

512
00:20:37,350 --> 00:20:38,680
a self-made pen holder.

513
00:20:38,800 --> 00:20:40,600
I was afraid he would dislike it.

514
00:20:41,470 --> 00:20:43,900
Later I found he liked it.

515
00:20:45,860 --> 00:20:53,880
[Linqi Oilfield No. 2 High School]

516
00:20:54,030 --> 00:20:54,890
You're coming.

517
00:20:54,980 --> 00:20:55,540
Dude.

518
00:20:55,670 --> 00:20:57,440
Please open the gate for me.

519
00:20:57,470 --> 00:20:58,790
I'm here to deliver something.

520
00:20:58,790 --> 00:20:59,790
Are you going

521
00:20:59,790 --> 00:21:01,030
to bring food to Director Xiao again?

522
00:21:01,030 --> 00:21:02,640
Yes. Yes.

523
00:21:03,250 --> 00:21:04,090
Hold on.

524
00:22:26,950 --> 00:22:27,830
Who is it?

525
00:22:28,440 --> 00:22:29,280
It's me.

526
00:22:36,240 --> 00:22:37,090
Ms. Han.

527
00:22:39,050 --> 00:22:40,300
What's up?

528
00:22:40,870 --> 00:22:42,030
You didn't get a chance

529
00:22:42,030 --> 00:22:43,130
to eat the Eight-Treasure Duck at noon.

530
00:22:43,130 --> 00:22:45,260
I made another one for you especially.

531
00:22:46,880 --> 00:22:50,140
It's late now and you were still preparing for the lessons?

532
00:22:50,460 --> 00:22:51,650
Mr. Jia,

533
00:22:52,650 --> 00:22:53,270
you shouldn't send anything

534
00:22:53,270 --> 00:22:54,790
to me anymore.

535
00:22:54,900 --> 00:22:56,340
I'm Miaomiao's teacher.

536
00:22:56,590 --> 00:22:57,310
It's my duty

537
00:22:57,310 --> 00:22:58,540
to care about her.

538
00:22:59,190 --> 00:23:00,490
Don't be so distant.

539
00:23:00,620 --> 00:23:02,230
Look how hard you work every day.

540
00:23:02,230 --> 00:23:03,630
Your face looks slimmer.

541
00:23:04,220 --> 00:23:05,510
If you don't take good care of yourself,

542
00:23:05,510 --> 00:23:06,070
how can you

543
00:23:06,070 --> 00:23:07,150
manage such a large class?

544
00:23:07,150 --> 00:23:07,790
Right?

545
00:23:43,780 --> 00:23:45,110
If you keep doing this,

546
00:23:45,110 --> 00:23:47,190
others might get the wrong idea about us.

547
00:23:47,190 --> 00:23:48,550
Speaking of this,

548
00:23:48,580 --> 00:23:49,270
I'll have to explain it

549
00:23:49,270 --> 00:23:50,390
to you later.

550
00:23:51,160 --> 00:23:52,350
This duck

551
00:23:52,370 --> 00:23:53,970
would taste better.

552
00:23:54,630 --> 00:23:55,700
Actually, the one I sent at noon

553
00:23:55,700 --> 00:23:56,780
was for you.

554
00:23:56,830 --> 00:23:58,430
But I didn't expect to meet Director Xiao.

555
00:23:58,430 --> 00:23:59,270
She was being self-deluding,

556
00:23:59,270 --> 00:24:00,100
like a peacock spreading its tail feathers in a display.

557
00:24:00,100 --> 00:24:01,110
She thought it was made for her.

558
00:24:01,110 --> 00:24:02,370
So she ate it directly.

559
00:24:02,660 --> 00:24:04,390
By the way, don't get me wrong.

560
00:24:04,540 --> 00:24:06,370
I only have respect for Director Xiao.

561
00:24:06,370 --> 00:24:08,030
I don't have feelings for her.

562
00:24:08,340 --> 00:24:09,410
Mr. Jia,

563
00:24:09,540 --> 00:24:11,070
I really don't understand.

564
00:24:11,610 --> 00:24:12,480
It doesn't matter.

565
00:24:12,480 --> 00:24:13,670
We have plenty of time.

566
00:24:13,670 --> 00:24:14,690
We can talk about it later.

567
00:24:14,690 --> 00:24:16,120
But the duck is getting cold.

568
00:24:16,120 --> 00:24:17,090
Sit down and eat.

569
00:24:17,110 --> 00:24:19,630
No need. I'm not hungry.

570
00:24:19,850 --> 00:24:21,140
You have to even if you're not.

571
00:24:21,140 --> 00:24:22,890
You didn't get a chance to eat the one I sent at noon.

572
00:24:22,890 --> 00:24:23,640
But it's okay.

573
00:24:23,640 --> 00:24:24,930
Let's just take it as my first try.

574
00:24:24,930 --> 00:24:26,060
Without that one,

575
00:24:26,080 --> 00:24:27,690
I couldn't make a better one.

576
00:24:27,850 --> 00:24:28,670
It's really delicious.

577
00:24:28,670 --> 00:24:29,470
Try it.

578
00:24:30,310 --> 00:24:30,910
By the way,

579
00:24:31,380 --> 00:24:34,030
well, when we were at the office this noon,

580
00:24:34,390 --> 00:24:36,420
I knew you kept a distance from me deliberately.

581
00:24:36,420 --> 00:24:37,470
I understand.

582
00:24:37,490 --> 00:24:38,890
Since you understand,

