00:36:09,120 --> 00:36:10,090
What do you mean?

871
00:36:10,110 --> 00:36:11,930
Do you really think I'm a big eater?

872
00:36:11,930 --> 00:36:12,490
No. No.

873
00:36:12,520 --> 00:36:14,360
I-I didn't mean that!

874
00:36:14,670 --> 00:36:16,620
I just want

875
00:36:16,650 --> 00:36:17,530
to clean the air

876
00:36:17,560 --> 00:36:18,710
with this dish.

877
00:36:20,120 --> 00:36:21,070
I didn't expect

878
00:36:21,070 --> 00:36:23,470
the Boiled Sliced Pork would be so helpful.

879
00:36:24,190 --> 00:36:25,220
The point is

880
00:36:25,220 --> 00:36:26,430
there's no misunderstanding between us.

881
00:36:26,430 --> 00:36:27,550
I'm afraid there's a misunderstanding

882
00:36:27,550 --> 00:36:28,880
between you and Ms. Han.

883
00:36:30,510 --> 00:36:31,390
Well, I...

884
00:36:32,590 --> 00:36:33,430
Hurry up.

885
00:36:33,740 --> 00:36:34,990
Ms. Han will be off work soon.

886
00:36:34,990 --> 00:36:37,250
You should bring it to her while it's hot.

887
00:36:37,740 --> 00:36:38,470
Director...

888
00:36:41,110 --> 00:36:42,120
What should I do?

889
00:36:44,410 --> 00:36:47,080
[Teaching Building]

890
00:37:17,010 --> 00:37:18,150
It's 9:20 a.m.

891
00:37:18,150 --> 00:37:20,190
Shouldn't they be here at nine o'clock?

892
00:37:20,190 --> 00:37:21,850
Qiang Xiaowa is not here either.

893
00:37:21,850 --> 00:37:23,510
They should be here together.

894
00:37:24,370 --> 00:37:25,170
What's wrong?

895
00:37:26,510 --> 00:37:28,240
Why haven't they been here yet?

896
00:37:29,820 --> 00:37:31,420
Don't be nervous. Calm down.

897
00:37:32,030 --> 00:37:34,070
In my opinion, there's only one possibility.

898
00:37:34,070 --> 00:37:34,750
Qiang Xiaowa

899
00:37:34,750 --> 00:37:35,800
hasn't tutored her well.

900
00:37:35,800 --> 00:37:36,870
He's afraid Hua'er can't pass the exams.

901
00:37:36,870 --> 00:37:37,570
So they won't come.

902
00:37:37,570 --> 00:37:39,120
I was like this when I was a junior.

903
00:37:39,120 --> 00:37:39,830
To avoid the chemistry exam,

904
00:37:39,830 --> 00:37:41,180
I hid in the toilet all morning.

905
00:37:41,180 --> 00:37:42,490
Do you think others are also a loser

906
00:37:42,490 --> 00:37:43,290
just like you?

907
00:37:44,210 --> 00:37:46,090
Fine, let's wait and see.

908
00:37:47,670 --> 00:37:49,510
Speaking of the toilet, my stomach hurts again.

909
00:37:49,510 --> 00:37:50,420
Enough.

910
00:37:50,440 --> 00:37:52,310
You've been to the toilet three times this morning.

911
00:37:52,310 --> 00:37:53,530
You're not the one who's going to take the exams.

912
00:37:53,530 --> 00:37:55,060
Stop pretending like that.

913
00:37:59,060 --> 00:37:59,700
Xiaowa.

914
00:38:00,520 --> 00:38:01,130
What...

915
00:38:02,280 --> 00:38:03,310
What happened to your face?

916
00:38:03,310 --> 00:38:04,840
Did you fight with someone?

917
00:38:05,440 --> 00:38:06,670
Why are you here alone?

918
00:38:06,670 --> 00:38:07,600
Where is Hua'er?

919
00:38:08,980 --> 00:38:10,710
She can't make it to take the exams.

920
00:38:10,710 --> 00:38:12,990
See? Facts speak louder than words.

921
00:38:13,990 --> 00:38:14,990
Shut up.

922
00:38:15,020 --> 00:38:15,700
Shut up.

923
00:38:21,690 --> 00:38:23,020
What on earth happened?

924
00:38:25,040 --> 00:38:26,830
Leave the problems first if you can't solve them temporarily.

925
00:38:26,830 --> 00:38:28,610
You'll take the Chinese and math exams during the same period.

926
00:38:28,610 --> 00:38:30,000
Remember to leave some time for your composition.

927
00:38:30,000 --> 00:38:31,280
Don't worry, Xiaowa.

928
00:38:31,320 --> 00:38:32,720
I can do well in the exams.

929
00:38:35,080 --> 00:38:35,570
Hua'er.

930
00:38:35,590 --> 00:38:36,650
-Hua'er! -Eggs...

931
00:38:36,830 --> 00:38:38,220
You little brat!

932
00:38:38,310 --> 00:38:39,110
You sneaked back

933
00:38:39,110 --> 00:38:40,170
to find him?

934
00:38:40,190 --> 00:38:40,940
Li! Li!

935
00:38:40,970 --> 00:38:41,460
Uncle.

936
00:38:41,480 --> 00:38:42,480
Li. Li.

937
00:38:42,510 --> 00:38:44,910
Hua'er's back because she wants to go to school.

938
00:38:44,910 --> 00:38:46,290
We've talked to the Oilfield's middle school

939
00:38:46,290 --> 00:38:47,190
for her.

940
00:38:47,460 --> 00:38:48,410
She's going to take exams today.

941
00:38:48,410 --> 00:38:49,490
Shut up!

942
00:38:49,780 --> 00:38:50,780
She doesn't need to go to school!

943
00:38:50,780 --> 00:38:52,190
She has gone to school for so many years! Isn't that enough?

944
00:38:52,190 --> 00:38:52,890
I

945
00:38:52,920 --> 00:38:54,230
have never been to school.

946
00:38:54,230 --> 00:38:56,710
But it doesn't cause any problems for me to get a job and make money.

947
00:38:56,710 --> 00:38:57,990
Go back to Guangdong to work.

948
00:38:57,990 --> 00:38:58,990
I've made a deal with your boss.

949
00:38:58,990 --> 00:39:00,260
Go back and keep working there.

950
00:39:00,260 --> 00:39:02,270
Dad, Mom, I want to go to school.

951
00:39:02,300 --> 00:39:03,600
After I finish my studies,

952
00:39:03,600 --> 00:39:05,330
I'll make money to support you.

953
00:39:05,360 --> 00:39:06,670
After she graduates from school,

954
00:39:06,670 --> 00:39:08,180
she'll earn much more than now!

955
00:39:08,180 --> 00:39:10,050
I don't care whether the times have changed.

956
00:39:10,050 --> 00:39:11,200
she will work

957
00:39:11,230 --> 00:39:12,350
and earn money

958
00:39:12,350 --> 00:39:13,360
for her brother's marriage!

959
00:39:13,360 --> 00:39:14,570
What does it

960
00:39:14,610 --> 00:39:15,840
have to do with her?

961
00:39:15,870 --> 00:39:16,500
What were you saying?

962
00:39:16,500 --> 00:39:17,430
That's her biological brother!

963
00:39:17,430 --> 00:39:19,560
You think it has nothing to do with her?

964
00:39:20,190 --> 00:39:21,380
Her brother went out to work

965
00:39:21,380 --> 00:39:22,620
before he graduated from elementary school.

966
00:39:22,620 --> 00:39:23,660
With our help,

967
00:39:23,690 --> 00:39:24,750
she finished her middle school.

968
00:39:24,750 --> 00:39:25,840
Others' daughters

969
00:39:25,860 --> 00:39:27,230
have long gone out to make money.

970
00:39:27,230 --> 00:39:28,350
Do you still think it has nothing to do with her?

971
00:39:28,350 --> 00:39:29,590
Cut the crap! Take her away!

972
00:39:29,590 --> 00:39:30,230
Move away!

973
00:39:30,760 --> 00:39:31,800
Move away!

974
00:39:31,910 --> 00:39:32,490
Come with me!

975
00:39:32,490 --> 00:39:32,930
No!

976
00:39:32,960 --> 00:39:34,310
Hua'er is good at studying!

977
00:39:34,310 --> 00:39:35,580
I can't let you cause any delays in her studies!

978
00:39:35,580 --> 00:39:36,190
Move away!

979
00:39:36,210 --> 00:39:37,010
No!

980
00:39:38,980 --> 00:39:39,460
Dad!

981
00:39:39,480 --> 00:39:40,010
You brat!

982
00:39:40,030 --> 00:39:40,880
Even your grandpa

983
00:39:40,880 --> 00:39:41,790
can't control me!

984
00:39:41,790 --> 00:39:43,510
Who do you think you are?

985
00:39:43,530 --> 00:39:44,370
You little brat!

986
00:39:44,370 --> 00:39:45,480
I'll kill you!

987
00:39:46,060 --> 00:39:47,300
-I'll kill you! -I'm not going to school!

988
00:39:47,300 --> 00:39:48,610
Li! Li!

989
00:39:48,650 --> 00:39:50,250
I won't go to school anymore!

990
00:39:52,030 --> 00:39:54,190
I'll go back to Guangdong with you now.

991
00:39:54,800 --> 00:39:56,800
Will you? Have you made up your mind?

992
00:40:04,930 --> 00:40:05,610
Let's go!

993
00:40:07,710 --> 00:40:08,760
Let's go home.

994
00:40:10,840 --> 00:40:11,720
Hua'er!

995
00:40:12,050 --> 00:40:13,850
Please extend my thanks to them!

996
00:40:15,060 --> 00:40:17,230
Brother, everyone has their fate.

997
00:40:17,480 --> 00:40:19,880
Everyone has their own way of living a life.

998
00:40:20,230 --> 00:40:21,380
If this continues,

999
00:40:21,400 --> 00:40:22,510
I'll get you into trouble.

1000
00:40:22,510 --> 00:40:24,140
And I'll feel more guilty.

1001
00:40:24,750 --> 00:40:26,550
Fate can be changed

1002
00:40:26,580 --> 00:40:27,620
through efforts!

1003
00:40:27,990 --> 00:40:29,430
Don't worry, Xiaowa.

1004
00:40:29,690 --> 00:40:31,390
Although I can't go to school,

1005
00:40:31,430 --> 00:40:32,840
I will never

1006
00:40:32,860 --> 00:40:34,250
give up studying.

1007
00:40:34,270 --> 00:40:35,760
I can teach myself.

1008
00:40:36,220 --> 00:40:36,940
Let's go!

1009
00:40:37,950 --> 00:40:38,680
Let's go.

1010
00:41:13,930 --> 00:41:14,970
If possible,

1011
00:41:15,290 --> 00:41:16,730
I can talk to her parents.

1012
00:41:17,210 --> 00:41:19,340
I don't believe I can't persuade them.

1013
00:41:19,960 --> 00:41:21,280
They have left.

1014
00:41:27,470 --> 00:41:28,670
Thank you, Director.

1015
00:41:32,930 --> 00:41:34,080
Thank you, Mr. Gao.

1016
00:41:38,700 --> 00:41:39,590
Thank you.

1017
00:41:44,580 --> 00:41:45,780
What the heck is this?

1018
00:41:46,260 --> 00:41:47,480
It's all in vain.

1019
00:41:56,770 --> 00:41:57,550
I believe Hua'er

1020
00:41:57,550 --> 00:41:59,410
will make it by teaching herself.

1021
00:42:04,570 --> 00:42:06,380
I will study hard in the future.

1022
00:42:08,240 --> 00:42:10,080
I have to

1023
00:42:11,930 --> 00:42:14,260
cherish the opportunity others dream of.

1024
00:42:22,390 --> 00:42:24,070
We all thought as long as we worked hard,

1025
00:42:24,070 --> 00:42:25,670
there would be good results,

1026
00:42:25,790 --> 00:42:26,750
and as long as we grew toward the sun,

1027
00:42:26,750 --> 00:42:28,550
we could all become a sunflower.

1028
00:42:28,900 --> 00:42:30,340
But in the real world,

1029
00:42:30,390 --> 00:42:31,720
the sun is always there.

1030
00:42:31,750 --> 00:42:32,700
However,

1031
00:42:32,940 --> 00:42:34,230
not every flower

1032
00:42:34,260 --> 00:42:36,190
has a chance to grow toward the sun.

1033
00:42:36,570 --> 00:42:38,320
Uncle has never got a chance

1034
00:42:38,350 --> 00:42:39,750
to treat Han Shu to a meal.

1035
00:42:40,170 --> 00:42:42,770
Hua'er couldn't make it to take exams.

1036
00:42:43,670 --> 00:42:45,060
This is the first time

1037
00:42:45,540 --> 00:42:46,730
I've felt helpless.

1038
00:42:47,960 --> 00:42:49,690
With the help of so many people,

1039
00:42:49,820 --> 00:42:51,100
the kid still

1040
00:42:51,120 --> 00:42:52,400
didn't make it to go to school.

1041
00:42:52,400 --> 00:42:53,240
Hua'er,

1042
00:42:54,010 --> 00:42:56,130
no matter where you go in the future,

1043
00:42:56,720 --> 00:42:57,510
I hope

1044
00:42:57,550 --> 00:42:58,300
you can

1045
00:42:58,770 --> 00:43:00,230
grow up safely and nicely.

1046
00:43:01,050 --> 00:43:01,890
We

1047
00:43:02,520 --> 00:43:03,560
will meet again.
